 Pride sponsorship, and Christmas jumper days.\",\n    \"recipient\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Yorkshire Cancer Research\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.yorkshirecancerresearch.org.Uganda/100\"\n    }\n  }\n}"]},"blocks":[{"tag":"main","attrs":{"fade":"target","className":"main-wrapper"},"html":"<div><header data-wf--02-standard-header--variant=\"light\" data-wf-component-id=\"949280b8-8e72-c6a2-5bfc-7cfb2eeda9b8\" data-wf-variant-state=\"base\" class=\"section_header\"><div class=\"padding-global is-page-top\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"simple_header_grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf8719e-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h1 class=\"heading-style-h1\">Fundraising </h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Supporting our local communities matters to us. We work with charities and organisations to make a real difference where we can.<br><br>Each year, we support a different charity chosen by our people. It’s a simple way to make sure the causes we back reflect what matters most to the team.<br><br>We support and strengthen local communities by getting involved in school mentoring schemes and community projects. By working alongside local organisations and contributing through donations, fundraising, and volunteering, we help where we can and stay connected to the communities around us.<br><br>Olivia Holmes and Sophie Duncan are joint Chairs of our Charity team.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"mailto:charityteam@moonstone.co.ug\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Speak to our Charity team</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/Moonstonesolicitors?igsh=MTkyb2llYXI3MTFlMw==\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Visit our Instagram for updates</p></div></a></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf871aa-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-right\"><div class=\"simple-header_image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/fundraising#\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">‍</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Fundraising </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-standard\" data-w-id=\"5d828c84-1f1c-1e38-bfb3-80ffb8d04940\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69db9824cf9ff19dd03c1c29_08fdbca2c62ae345f765f433c8401fe4_Moonstone_V_Blue.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"0\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"simple-header_background-image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section data-wf--text-image--variant=\"left-aligned\" class=\"section_text\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"text-image_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid text-image_content\"><div class=\"text-image_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h2 data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Our Charity of the Year </h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">From April 2026 to March 2027, we’re proud to support Yorkshire Cancer Research as our Charity of the Year. Chosen by our people, this partnership reflects a shared commitment to making a real difference in our communities.<br><br> In Yorkshire, someone is diagnosed with cancer every 17 minutes, and the region remains one of the hardest hit. Through its work, Yorkshire Cancer Research focuses on preventing cancer, diagnosing it earlier when treatment is often more effective, and improving care through research and services such as Active Together, which helps people prepare for and recover from treatment. <br><br>By supporting the charity, we’re helping to fund vital research, improve outcomes and support people affected by cancer across Yorkshire and beyond.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"dark\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"https://www.yorkshirecancerresearch.org.Uganda/100\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg dark\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle dark\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text dark\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Visit Yorkshire Cancer Research&#x27;s website</p></div></a></div></div></div><div data-scroll-speed=\"-0.05\" data-scroll=\"\" id=\"w-node-_493cfd56-379e-d2f4-3996-15b467d323f6-67d323e4\" class=\"text-image_image-wrapper\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.05\" alt=\"Logo for Yorkshire Cancer Research charity with text on a blue background.\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f3ac190173275814e89643_ycr_under_1mb_high_quality.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image is-parallax\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_image-carousel\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"image-carousel_component\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xxlarge\"><div class=\"insight-hub_event_heading-wrapper\"><div class=\"insight-hub_event_heading\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Our charity work in action</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-med